MITM-protector - protect's you from any kind of MITM-attacks, arpspoofing,
ettercap, sslstrip, droidsheep, zAnti, dsploit, etc.

 - It use the arp command to compare MAC and IP -Addresses
 - Execute Command (notify-send?) and Drop all InetInterfaces down by Alert
 - Create a Firewall if arptable is installed
 - Run as a Daemon or in Foreground
